OL,5, Broadcaster Nicky Campbell has told the
OL,6, Scottish Child Abuse Inquiry of the    
OL,7, sexual abuse he says he experienced at 
OL,8, the hands of a teacher.                
OL,10,FThe BBC Radio 5Live presenter described
OL,11,Fhis experiences at Edinburgh Academy in
OL,12,Fthe 1960s and 70s.                     
OL,14,FHe said he was also beaten by one of   
OL,15,Fhis teachers and he witnessed the      
OL,16,Fsexual abuse of a friend.              
OL,18,FHe is one of a number of former pupils 
OL,19,Fof the private school who are giving   
OL,20,Fevidence to the long-running inquiry.  
